OL,3,CMP backs proposal to teach Mindfulness
OL,4,Cin schools
OL,6,FThe MP for Warrington North has said
OL,7,Fthat children would benefit from being
OL,8,Ftaught mindfulness lessons after
OL,9,FBrianna Ghey's murder.
OL,11,FLabour's Charlotte Nichols said
OL,12,Fteaching mindfulness would also
OL,13,Fcreative positive change for not just
OL,14,Fpupils, but staff across the country
OL,15,Fand promote "empathy, compassion and
OL,16,Fkindness" in society.
OL,18,FThe charity Mind defines Mindfulness
OL,19,Fas a calming technique which involves
OL,20,Fnoticing what is happening in the
OL,21,Fpresent moment without judgment.
