OL,6,FMs Nichols, MP for Warrington North,
OL,7,Ftold a : "Brianna Ghey was sassy,
OL,8,Fbeautiful, kind, courageous and
OL,9,Fauthentically herself. She was loved
OL,10,Ffiercely and her was death unspeakably
OL,11,Ftragic.
OL,13,F"No parent should ever have to bury
OL,14,Ftheir child but to have gone through
OL,15,Fwhat Esther has, and have the drive to
OL,16,Fseek positive change in the wake of
OL,17,Fthat takes extraordinary courage and
OL,18,Fcompassion.
