OL,6,F"is perhaps the most remarkable person
OL,7,FI have ever met but she doesn't want
OL,8,Fthe sympathy or pity of those here
OL,9,Ftoday, but a commitment to standing
OL,10,Falongside her and our community in
OL,11,Fdelivering a lasting legacy for her
OL,12,Fdaughter.
OL,14,F"We want to promote empathy,
OL,15,Fcompassion and kindness throughout
OL,16,Fsociety, and I hope today's debate
OL,17,Fbrings us one step closer to achieving
OL,18,Fthis with a modest, evidence-based ask
OL,19,Fto put mindfulness onto the national
OL,20,Fcurriculum for the benefit of pupils,
OL,21,Fstaff and our country."
