OL,6,FSchools minister Damian Hinds
OL,7,Frecognised the work of , who was sat
OL,8,Fin Westminster Hall for the debate on
OL,9,FWednesday 7 February.
OL,11,FMr Hinds said: "Her ambition to
OL,12,Fpromote empathy, compassion and
OL,13,Fresilience through the Peace In Mind
OL,14,Fcampaign is one we can and do all
OL,15,Fcommend.
OL,17,F"There are few things more critical
OL,18,Fthan the happiness of our children.
