OL,6,F"The Government actively explored
OL,7,Fapproaches that could improve young
OL,8,Fpeople's mental health and wellbeing,
OL,9,Fsuch as mindfulness interventions."
OL,11,FMr Hinds added: "There is evidence of
OL,12,Fthe benefits of mindfulness, and I
OL,13,Fknow many schools will feel a positive
OL,14,Fimpact on their students from
OL,15,Fprogrammes like the one provided by
OL,16,Fthe Mindfulness in Schools Project.
OL,18,F"We should also remember that it might
OL,19,Fnot be right for everyone ` for every
OL,20,Fschool or every individual within a
OL,21,Fschool.
