OL,6,F"Schools should retain flexibility to
OL,7,Fchoose the interventions that suit
OL,8,Ftheir pupils and their own local
OL,9,Fcontext, supported by high-quality
OL,10,Fevidence and guidance."
OL,12,FMr Hinds said the Government is
OL,13,Foffering all state schools and
OL,14,Fcolleges a grant to train a senior
OL,15,Fmental health lead by next year,
OL,16,Fnoting more than 14,400 have claimed
OL,17,Fsuch funding so far.
